{"tid":2491412,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[片] 疑似愛國人士追打記者","createTime":"2021-04-16T09:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T13:09:48.000Z","uid":289214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3b7d509470e631a3ac9069272737e6a88c431bb4","tid":2491412,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"疑似愛國人士追打記者<br />\n【疑似愛國人士追打記者】<br />\n8.18 非法集結案今午在西九龍裁判法院判刑，據網媒《幽光》報道，下午 3 時許，一名身穿「中國人不吃這一套」的疑似愛國人士，在法院外近發祥街交界，追打在場的記者，包括《幽光》的記者及另一網媒記者，片段顯示該名男子在現場指罵記者一段時間後，突然衝前打人，再轉身打另一名記者，之後急跑逃走，而據《幽光》報道，當時在<span class=\"red\"><strong>附近戒備的警員無追捕該男子</strong></span>。<br />\n片段來源：幽光 Luminant Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/4V5tIWTz1V/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F4V5tIWTz1V%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=51bba2e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/4V5tIWTz1V/</a>"},{"pid":"ed07f9b5461357bf989720912c0ffdbbfc069454","tid":2491412,"uid":170949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4243af2fe119b3e9ca1edaeac364ec528e8a557","tid":2491412,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"林鄭琴日放風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日就做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e17e3b61c1e6ae2a9ba80c5b7f51d0d6f857009","tid":2491412,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3863a30749e036fac0be70e09aac30128ec332","tid":2491412